  <brief_title>First-in-Human Single Ascending and Multiple Dose of GLPG0259</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double Blind, Placebo-controlled Trial for the Assessment of Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics (PK), and Pharmacodynamics (PD) of Single Ascending and Multiple Oral Doses of GLPG0259 in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
